                                                                    JUnit Class

Unit testing:-  Unit testing is a level of software testing where individual units/code of a software are tested.

Junit is an Unit testing framework.
 Junit 3 --> Strictly typed
 Junit 4 --> Advanced, less strictly typed.

 JUnit --> XUnit
                ---NUnit  --> asp
                ---PyUnit --> python
                ---JUnit  --> Java
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
JUnit 3
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 YOu have to extend TestCase class for every test class you write
 ClassName has to be meaningful
 TestClass should contains Test along with className

 Every method should contain test before methodName

 ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 JUnit 4
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 No need of writing extending a TestCase class
 No need of writing  test before every method

Annotations: Form of Metadata
                  data about data

Assertions : affirming statement
                       expected value, output

